						               													<description>War &amp;amp; Pieces is the ultimate family game of building, tactical skill, and destruction. Each player builds a fortress with blocks and must knock the other player(s) fortresses down by launching a catapult.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Each player begins with 50 building blocks and 5 special soldier blocks, and constructs a fortress on a game mat. Rules are simple, solider blocks cannot touch the mat and building blocks that touch the map must be sideways.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Players take turns launching the stone catapult, or the ballista at an opposing player's fortress. If a solider block gets knocked down, that unlocks a special power that may benefit or harm the shooter. Players who lose all their solider blocks are eliminated. Last player standing wins!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;War &amp;amp; Pieces is created by YouTube Superstar and family man, Roman Atwood, in conjunction with Studio71 and Justin Gary, founder of Blade Entertainment.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
